
*cgroup* stands for (Kernel) *Control Group*.

The kernel control group *hierarchy* is exposed under `→ Linux/fhs/sys/fs/cgroup`.

sa:
  `→ Linux/fhs/proc/pid/cgroups`

  `→ Linux/kernel/source/kernel/cgroup_c`

  `→ Linux/kernel/source/Documentation/cgroup-v1`,
  `→ Linux/kernel/source/Documentation/admin-guide/cgroups-v2_rst`

   `man 7 cgroups` 
